🧭 NAVIGATION UX (CRITICAL IMPROVEMENT)

The system MUST enforce a 3-step hierarchical selection flow:

STEP 1: Namespace selection (Dropdown)

- Clean dropdown UI
- searchable
- grouped if needed

STEP 2: Deployment selection (Dropdown)

- filtered by selected namespace
- shows deployment health indicator

STEP 3: Pod selection (Dropdown)

- filtered by deployment
- shows pod status (Running / CrashLoop / etc.)

RULE:

- User NEVER types names manually
- Everything is selected via UI only
- Selection flow must feel like a guided debugger setup

